                        Our mission is to make premium products and professional services accessible to everyone, while maintaining the highest standards of quality and authenticity.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light)); height: 400px; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 8rem; opacity: 0.2;">
