                <p>What drives us forward</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                    <div class="card border-0 h-100">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <div class="feature-icon" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                                <i class="bi bi-gem"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h5>Quality</h5>
                            <p class="text-muted-custom mb-0">We never compromise on quality. Every product is carefully selected and tested.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                    <div class="card border-0 h-100">
